{"tid":1875353,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"加航3月停多倫多香港直航 延長停飛北京上海至3月27日","createTime":"2020-02-11T17:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T19:37:04.000Z","uid":28114,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"369d2d56f6d7fe94c5498435abef0a6392100056","tid":1875353,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.singtao.ca/wp-content/uploads/rtnews/2020/02/Apps_600x350_2020-02-11_101431.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.singtao.ca%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Frtnews%2F2020%2F02%2FApps_600x350_2020-02-11_101431.jpg&h=22af2779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加拿大航空宣布，延長暫停往來中國北京及上海的航班服務至2020年3月27日，至於往來多倫多至香港的直航航班，亦會由3月1日至27日暫停服務。<br />\n<br />\n加航表示，延長暫停北京及上海的航班班次，仍有待政府批准。<br />\n<br />\n加航亦表示，由3月1日至27日，加航將暫停往來多倫多至香港的每日直航航班，以反映市場需求減少的情況；至於往來溫哥華至香港的每日直航航班，將會接載原先訂下多倫多直飛香港的預訂乘客。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.singtao.ca/wp-content/uploads/rtnews/2020/02/2020-02-11_102601-600x375.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.singtao.ca%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Frtnews%2F2020%2F02%2F2020-02-11_102601-600x375.jpg&h=5c7891a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加航通常每周有14班飛往香港的航班，其中7班從多倫多出發，7班由溫哥華出發。<br />\n<br />\n加國政府於2020年1月29日發出公布，勸告國民如非必要，不要到中國旅遊，而加航於2月開始暫停往來北京及上海的航班。<br />\n<br />\n加航表示，會繼續與加拿大公共衛生局、加拿大運輸部門及全球事務部門協商，密切監視疫情的發展，以便調整航班服務。<br />\n<br />\n加航有提供從多倫多、滿地可及溫哥華直飛北京及上海的航班。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">至於是次改動，對往來台灣的航班不會受影響。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singtao.ca/4088988/2020-02-11/news-加航3月停多倫多香港直航+延長停飛北京上海至3月27日/?variant=zh-hk&amp;appedition=toronto\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.ca%2F4088988%2F2020-02-11%2Fnews-%E5%8A%A0%E8%88%AA3%E6%9C%88%E5%81%9C%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%AB%E5%A4%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9B%B4%E8%88%AA%2B%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7%E5%81%9C%E9%A3%9B%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E8%87%B33%E6%9C%8827%E6%97%A5%2F%3Fvariant%3Dzh-hk%26appedition%3Dtoronto&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2Bfkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=ade6a321\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtao.ca/4088988/2020-02-11/news-加航3月停多倫多香港直航+延長停飛北京上海至3月27日/?variant=zh-hk&amp;appedition=toronto</a>"},{"pid":"4403e251f8916ce2a32e5cf93f4eb0cb8215c2d4","tid":1875353,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:42:13.000Z","msg":"林鄭死不封關，各國就封你關<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7dd3c0822599b4f8fc5f2c0b0935444f798af52","tid":1875353,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持唔封關 攬炒"},{"pid":"31f3df33c675571b9d22678cfbeabad3f9f175d7","tid":1875353,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:52:25.000Z","msg":"林鄭死不封關嘅後果，就係各國對香港呢個地方嘅衛生防疫安全成疑<br />\n前幾日先講維珍cut澳洲飛去香港嘅直航<br />\n而家又到加航<br />\n各國借啲意cut吓又一班 cut吓又多一班直航<br />\n變相封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n逃生門即將關上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611d853a53e830320af8dcc9b98ce56cffd7291c","tid":1875353,"uid":273218,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:55:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r38Ud00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr38Ud00.jpg&h=8c3044e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fxpgsk2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffxpgsk2.jpg&h=9853a803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實早幾日經過機場<br />\n都比平時少左9成人<br />\n眼見有7，8成航班取消左<br />\n有d驚訝，點解可以咁低調新聞完全唔報<br />\n我發覺香港人好易被蒙在鼓裡"},{"pid":"452e609659004a90271f06548ce9